.Dd February 1, 2026
.Dt CRYPTO_STRERROR 3MONOCYPHER
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm crypto_strerror
.Nd error string for checked APIs
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In monocypher.h
.Ft const char *
.Fo crypto_strerror
.Fa "int err"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn crypto_strerror
maps
.Vt crypto_err
values to constant strings such as
.Dq CRYPTO_OK
or
.Dq CRYPTO_ERR_NULL .
.Pp
This helper is optional and only available when Monocypher is built with
.Dv MONOCYPHER_STRERROR=1
(or
.Dv STRERROR=1
when using the provided makefile).
.Sh RETURN VALUES
On success, a pointer to a constant string is returned.
Unknown error codes return
.Dq CRYPTO_ERR_UNKNOWN .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr crypto_random 3monocypher ,
.Xr intro 3monocypher
